reviews.title: Happy Days Are Here Again!
reviews.comment: This app is excellent and very user friendly for seniors like myself.  I am completely paperless now and just love seeing technology like this move forward.  Thank you First National of Omaha!
reviews.author: Kraston Scott

reviews.title: Finally!!!
reviews.comment: I have been waiting for this app since 2011. Im really excited. Seems pretty user friendly. I haven\'t used any deposit functions yet tho. It took them really long to make this app, I hope its worth waiting.
reviews.author: Bakhrom Oripov

reviews.title: Making Deposits
reviews.comment: Has anyone tried to make a deposit using this app as yet? I have a check I need to deposit and the app asks that you take a picture of the front and back of the check. When I go to do that, there is a little camera icon that appears, but for the life of me, I can\'t snap a photo. I keep depressing the camera icon, but I can\'t take a photo.  I use the camera on my phone every day to take pictures of my new grand baby. I think there is an error in the app.
